Broker - Class in fr.sorbonne_u.components.pubsub.components
A Broker is the heart of a PubSub component, in fact The PubSub class delegate all its operations to the Broker class.
Broker() - Constructor for class fr.sorbonne_u.components.pubsub.components.Broker
Creates a new broker instance with default parallelism equals to 10 for both the Broker.subscriberExecutor and the Broker.publisherExecutor.
Broker(int, int) - Constructor for class fr.sorbonne_u.components.pubsub.components.Broker
